## Package Management

- Use `uv` for package management.
- Use `uv add` and `uv remove` to change packages.

## Config Vars

Obtain config vars from Heroku using `heroku config -s > .env`.

## Executing Code

⚠️ If the .env file is not present, obtain config vars before executing code.

Use `uv run --env-file .env` to execute code.